  {
    "hotel_id": "486819",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/temple-da-nang_3/hotel/da-nang-vn.html",
    "name": "Temple Da Nang",
    "detail": "Looking to splurge from our typical budget for our last night in Da Nang, we were thrilled with the serenity that Temple afforded. There are only a handful of rooms on the property, all in a row with a beautiful little private patio that allows you to walk out onto a pristine stretch of white beach. We could even see Lady Buddha from our room! Arriving early, we were offered beverages while we waited in the beautiful restaurant overlooking the water. The breakfast was amazing, although we didn't have it in us to take full advantage of the made to order all you can eat selection! It was an absolutely romantic spot, with the private infinity pool offering an alternative to the beach which you pretty much have to yourself considering there are maybe 10 other patrons at the hotel on a given night. Will definitely book here again!",
